rnal, but they are supernatural as well </div><div class="t m2e x6 hb y140 ff5 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as natural. </div><div class="t m145 x1a hb y141 ff5 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What threatens the onward progress of the church today is not so much </div><div class="t m39 x6 hb y142 ff5 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">an external enemy, such as unbelief, liberalism, or worldliness (although </div><div class="t m146 x6 hb y143 ff5 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">we see these making inroads into the church). The greater threat to the </div><div class="t m147 x6 hc y144 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
